== SOURCE

https://www.polygon.com/22675796/fifa-22-hypermotion-motion-capture-new-realism

== AGENT

EA Sports Fifa 22

== GOAL

Animation in the new game

== DATA

They used data from the previous games and real life to see how football players approach the football what they did when they had it how many steps they took.

== METHODS

HyperMotion is the name they called this new aspect.

== RESULTS

A more realistic player gameplay where the game looks closer to real life football then ever before.

== ISSUES

It would be hard to transfer across to different sports game beside football

== SCORE

6

== COMMENTS

Seems like a very cool idea that would make gameplay much better an increase the quality of games in the future.
